title=Multiple Choice Questionnaire: For Online Learning
topics=<p>Key Topics Covered in this Tutorial:</p>\n<p>-&#9;A walk through the multiple-choice sample application</p>\n<p>-&#9;A walk through the multiple-choice editor</p>\n<p>-&#9;How to take apart and understand the scripts</p>\n<p></p>